		<td><b>scrolling / timing issue debugging</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />hi -- I'm having some issues debugging some scrolling / timing issues in my emulator. Right now I'm attempting to use Kung Fu to debug these issues, but wonder if there isn't something better. I'm not sure when the writes that Kung Fu does to the various scrolling registers are really supposed to be happening, for instance. What would people recommend for debugging these sorts of issues?
<br />
<br />Thanks for any assistance.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
	<tr>
