	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td width="10%" nowrap="nowrap">Post subject:&nbsp;</td>
		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />If you're making the emulator, you could tell what time the writes are happening, and maybe print the scanline and pixel number to stdout or a textbox every time there's a write to $2005 or $2006.
<br />Then compare it against another emulator with a debugger, so you can see if yours is different.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


